y-Suleymaniye (Report)]\n|team2=[[K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck\u00e7ekmece SK]]\n|goals1=[[Mehmet Leblebi|Mehmet]] {{goal|35}}<br>[[Latif Yal\u0131nl\u0131|Latif]] {{goal|59}}<br>[[Kemal Faruki|Kemal]] {{goal|71||88}}\n|goals2=[[Ru\u015fen Erman|Ru\u015fen]] {{goal|12}}\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stad\u0131]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee= \n|result=W\n|motm=\n|stack=yes\n}}\n{{footballbox  collapsible\n|date=April 24, 1931\n|time=\n|team1=[[\u00dcsk\u00fcdar Anadolu SK]]  \n|score=0 &ndash; 4\n|report=[http://www.mackolik.com/Mac/633392/Anadolu-Galatasaray (Report)]\n|team2=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray SK]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=[[Latif Yal\u0131nl\u0131|Latif]] {{goal|20}}<br>[[Kemal Faruki|Kemal]] {{goal|44}}<br>[[Latif Yal\u0131nl\u0131|Latif]] {{goal|61}}<br>[[Latif Yal\u0131nl\u0131|Latif]] {{goal|78}}\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stad\u0131]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W\n|motm=\n|stack=yes\n}}\n{{footballbox  collapsible\n|date=May 24, 1931\n|time=\n|team1=[[Beykoz 1908 S.K.D.]]  \n|score=2 &ndash; 2\n|report=[http://www.mackolik.com/Mac/633394/Beykoz-Galatasaray (Report)]\n|team2=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray SK]]\n|goals1=[[Salvator Vitali|Salvator]] {{goal|6}}<br>[[Latif Yal\u0131nl\u0131|Latif]] {{goal|75}}\n|goals2=[[Erc\u00fcment I\u015f\u0131l|Erc\u00fcment]] {{goal|4}}<br>[[Mehmet Leblebi|Mehmet]] {{goal|43}}\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stad\u0131]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee= [[Sait Selahattin Cihano\u011flu]]\n|result=D\n|motm=\n|stack=yes\n}}\n{{footballbox  collapsible\n|date=May 29, 1931\n|time=\n|team1=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray SK]]  \n|score=4 &ndash; 1\n|report=[http://www.mackolik.com/Mac/633425/Galatasaray-Vefa (Report)]\n|team2=[[Vefa SK]]\n|goals1=[[Mehmet Leblebi|Mehmet]] {{goal|40}}<br>[[Necdet Cici|Necdet]] {{goal|51||90}}<br>[[Erc\u00fcment I\u015f\u0131l|Erc\u00fcment]] {{goal|83}}\n|goals2=[[Muhte\u015fem Kural|Muhte\u015fem]] {{goal|75}}\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stad\u0131]], [[Istanbul]]\n|atte